item.description: I'd like a meeting similar to the last one, open to discussion. The time is a little earlier in the evening so I think we should make a dinner of it too. The restaurant seems reasonably priced. There is a parking garage on the next block west on Fore Street if there isn't good street parking... And you can check out their website www.bullfeeneys.com to download a menu or for directions, etc.
item.how_to_find_us: I made a reservation under "Raina Keim" - my last name is pronounced kime - rhymes with dime. Plus I'll wear my blue striped scarf!
item.name: February Meetup
